<p> Dear <%= @contact.name %>;</p>
<p>Thank you for your correspondence at <%= @contact.contact_time.strftime("%H:%M on %F") %>. Please quote this time and date in any subsequent communication with us on the subject.</p> It has been copied to a member of the team for action. 
<p>The following is the information you submitted.
</p>
<p>
<b>Type:</b>
<%= @contact.contact_type %>
</p>
<% if @contact.contact_county %>
<p>
<b>County:</b>
<%= ChapmanCode::name_from_code(@contact.contact_county) + '(' + @contact.contact_county + ')' %>
</p>
<% end %>
<p>
<b>Body:</b>
<%= @contact.body %>
</p>
<p>
<b>Screenshot:</b>
<% if @contact.screenshot_url %>
A screenshot was attached.<br>
<% else %>
No screenshot attached.
<% end %>
</p>
<p> The <%= MyopicVicar::Application.config.freexxx_display_name %> Team</p>
